      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Next Steps -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 py-12 mt-16 border-[3px] border-indigo-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Ready to Build Your Theater Company Website?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Here's what to do next:</p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 rounded-r-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">1. Compare Cultural Platforms</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">See how Squarespace and Webflow compare for theaters</p>
          <a href="/comparisons/squarespace-vs-webflow" class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline text-sm">Compare Squarespace vs Webflow â†’</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 rounded-r-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">2. Learn Theater Marketing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">Get our guide to theater company website marketing</p>
